            moved Amendment No. 7:
            <q>Page 7, line 14, at end insert ("or in relation to any assets vested in the official custodian for charities").</q>
            On Question, amendment agreed to.</p><p>
            Clause 17, as amended, agreed to.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
