      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0613P0-03462'>
        <a name='S5LV0613P0_20000607_GCR_72'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-alexander-irvine' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0613P0_20000607_GCR_72' title='Link to this speech by Mr Alexander Irvine' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
