      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0613P0-03530'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0613P0_20000607_GCR_140' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <q>In&#x2014;
        <ol>
        <li>(a) section 6(3) (Duchy of Cornwall Management Acts extended in relation to banking), and</li>
        <li>(b) section 11(2) (collective citation of Duchy of Cornwall Management Acts),</li>
        </ol>
        for "Duchy of Cornwall Management Acts 1868 to 1893" substitute "Duchy of Cornwall Management Acts 1863 to 1868".").</q>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0613P0-03531'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0613P0_20000607_GCR_141' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        On Question, amendment agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0613P0-03532'>
        <a name='S5LV0613P0_20000607_GCR_142'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-alexander-irvine' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
