          <p class='first-para'>
            moved Amendment No. 47:
            <q>Page 24, line 5, at end insert ("of that section").</q>
            The noble and learned Lord said: This amendment simply tidies up drafting. I beg to move.</p><p>
            On Question, amendment agreed to.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0613P0-03533'>
        <a name='S5LV0613P0_20000607_GCR_143'>  </a>
